Package: pwSEM
Title: Piecewise Structural Equation Modelling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bill", "Shipley", , "Bill.Shipley@USherbrooke.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7026-3880"))
Description: Conducts a dsep test of a directed, or mixed, acyclic graph 
    without latent variables (but possibly with implicitly marginalized or
    conditioned latent variables that create dependent errors)
       based on linear, generalized linear, or additive models
       with or without a nesting structure for the data.
